column1: #Text=The Dallas Mavericks ( 27 - 22 ) defeated the Brooklyn Nets ( 12 - 35 ) 91 - 79 on Wednesday at the American Airlines Arena in Dallas .
#Text=The Mavericks got off to a quick start in this one , out - scoring the Nets 25 - 18 in the first quarter .

#Text=The Mavericks were the superior shooters in this game , going 46 percent from the field and 38 percent from the three - point line , while the Nets finished at 36 percent from the floor and just 20 percent from deep .
#Text=The Mavericks were led by the duo of Brook Lopez and Chandler Parsons .
